    \new Score
    <<
        \context Staff = "Violin"

        {
            instrumentName = #"Violin"
        }
        {
            <<
                \context Voice = "voiceOne"
                {
                    \time 4/4
                    \clef "treble"
                    c'8
                    e'8
                    g'8
                    c''8
                    d''4
                    :32
                    ef''8
                    :16
                    e''16
                    :64
                    fs''16
                    :128
                }
                \context Voice = "TempoVoice"
                {
                    \tempo 4=60
                    s1
                }
            >>
            <<
                \context Voice = "voiceOne"
                {
                    f''4
                    :32
                    - \turn
                    ~
                    f''8.
                    :64
                    \fermata
                    c'''16
                    - \mordent
                    b''4
                    - \prall
                    bf''4
                    - \trill
                }
            >>
            <<
                \context Voice = "voiceOne"
                {
                    a''4
                    - \open
                    af''4
                    - \upbow
                    g''4
                    - \downbow
                    fs''4
                    - \stopped
                }
            >>
            <<
                \context Voice = "voiceOne"
                {
                    f''4
                    - \snappizzicato
                    <c' e' g' c''>4
                    \arpeggio
                    \arpeggioArrowDown

                    \arpeggio
